# Used when building from repo root (e.g. Dockerfile.local)
# Backup copy of apps/web — often contains huge .next / turbopack caches; never needed in the image.
apps/web.bak
# Next.js / Turbopack caches anywhere in the tree (root `.next` alone may not match nested paths on all Docker versions)
**/.next
**/.turbo
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
.gitignore
*.md
!docker/sandagent-claude/README.md
.dockerignore
.env
.env.*
*.log
.cursor
.vscode
apps/*/dist
packages/*/dist
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
benchmark-results
coverage
